                        jcr:description="&lt;p>In 2026, AbbVie will donate $241 for every strikeout thrown by a&amp;nbsp;Cubs&lt;i> &lt;/i>pitcher at Wrigley Field this season, honoring the roughly 241 Americans diagnosed with cancer every hour.&lt;sup>1&lt;/sup>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>AbbVie has pledged up to $250,000 per season in donations to support this cause.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-16-reg&quot;>1.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cancerstatisticscenter.cancer.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>http://cancerstatisticscenter.cancer.org&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                        jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-05-21T13:53:07.998-04:00"
                        jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        jcr:title="&lt;p>Donations to  &lt;br />&#xd;&#xa;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,102,245);&quot;>fight cancer &lt;/span>&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(71,159,248);&quot;> &lt;/span>&lt;br />&#xd;&#xa;with every  &lt;br />&#xd;&#xa;Cubs strikeout. &lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
